Thesaurus-DBI version 0.01
==========================

Thesaurus::DBI - Store and query synonyms (Thesaurus) in an SQL database.
This module ist a subclass of Thesaurus.pm and implements database storage.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Thesaurus
  DBI
  (DBD::mysql)

